    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, you gain the ability to twist your spells to suit your needs. You gain two of the following Metamagic options of your choice.</p><p>You gain another one at 6th, 10th, 13th and 17th level. You can use only one Metamagic option on a spell when you cast it, unless otherwise noted.</p><p>At 10th level in sorcerer you can swap out one of your Metamagic options of your choice whenever you complete a long rest. At 17th level in sorcerer, you can use multiple Metamagic options on a spell when you cast it.</p>",
